summary.span: 비 MSBuild 프로젝트 참조의 출력 파일을 확인합니다.

span.span: Determines the output files for non-MSBuild project references.

remarks.format: ## Remarks `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` 특수 속성 집합에서 검색 작업은 [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] 프로젝트 Guid와 관련 된 해당 출력의 목록에 대 한 IDE.The `ResolveNonMSBuildProjectOutput` task searches for a special property set by the [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] IDE for the list of project GUIDs and their associated outputs. IDE만 사전 확인 비-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 프로젝트 및 이러한 방식으로 구분 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 프로젝트 참조에서 비-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 참조 합니다.The IDE only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects and in this way separates [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references from non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] references. IDE의 목록을 반환 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] UnresolvedProjectReferences 서의 프로젝트입니다.The IDE returns the list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects as UnresolvedProjectReferences. 이렇게 하면 작업 더욱 강력한를 사용 하도록 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 조작 하는 메커니즘이 테이블만 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 와 같은 프로젝트 참조를 합니다.This enables the task to use more powerful [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] mechanisms to manipulate just the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references, such as. 매니페스트 파일 이름을 가져올 수에 대 한 참조의 특정 대상을 호출는 가능 하지 않습니다 혼합 목록이 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 및 비-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 프로젝트 참조 합니다.calling into specific targets of references to get the manifest file name, which would not be possible with a mixed list of [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] and non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] project references.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 이후 [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] 사전 확인 비-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 프로젝트 출력의 사전 확인 된 목록을 사용 하 여 확인할 수 없는 프로젝트 참조 항목에는 [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] 형식입니다.Since [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] only pre-resolves non-[!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] projects, the project reference items that could not be resolved using the pre-resolved list of outputs are in the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] format.
